一提的是，伯克希尔已连续第 10 个季度净减持股票，现金储备达到创纪录的 3477 亿美元（约合人民币 2.53 万亿元）。 大会主办地 CHI 会议中心座无虚席，有近 19700 人出席，创下历史新高。会议上，执掌公司 60 年的「奥马哈先知」妙语连珠，不仅谈到了现金储备、对美国未来的看法，也给年轻人提出了人生建议，「接班人」阿贝尔则谈到了自己的投资观点。 值得注意的是，在股东大会最后，巴菲特宣布他将在年底退休，格雷格·阿贝尔将成为伯克希尔新任 CEO。震惊全场！巴菲特宣布：年底退休，63 岁高管将接班！已囤积 2.5 万亿元现金，「美国财政问题令我害怕」，他还批评了特朗普关税政策 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b7445f0da97cfdcde10f865bc2dc480_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1902313765539668566"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIwp6u09L+qMteEAMaCTExNDc5NTM4MyCgq9vABjAAOOYCQBpyEzE5MDIzMTM3NjU1Mzk2Njg1NjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1746501181.853513", "card_id": "Q_12996127786", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 79}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "上班通勤在多久内可以接受啊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "毕业找工作，开始租房了 通勤时间在是半小时，一小时，一个半小时会比较好啊？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-0fd9d487d85a17c49e2e0f38b89ed3ee_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/12996127786"}}, "attached_info": "CkIIwp6u09L+qMteEAMaCTExMzU3NDcwMiDd5+S9BjAAOKUBQBtyCzEyOTk2MTI3Nzg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1746501181.853905", "card_id": "Q_653951784", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 3219}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么开了这么多会，却依然提升不了员工的激情？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-591dee58d4fd838e41b16086d7d9cfad_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "42 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "no